**Heir** | Attribute
__Basics__
Applied by the Monarch. Grants an additional vote on polls, and negates a vote.

__Formalized__
Passive Start Day:
  • Manipulate `Lynch` Poll (@Self has `-1` votes) (~PhaseAttribute)
  • Manipulate `Election` Poll (@Self has `-1` votes) (~PhaseAttribute)
  • Manipulate @Self's `special public voting power` to `1` (~PhaseAttribute)
